Title: Fix visualization of tags and labels in rule conditions
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1629445210
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

If host tag conditions were set in rules, the ruleset page has shown "Host:"
instead of "Host tag:".

Furthermore, the styling of host labels had slipped.
